articles.title: FEBRUARY 1976
articles.summary: This document lists the officers of an organization for February 1976, including the President, Vice-president, Secretary, and Treasurer, along with their respective names and contact numbers. It appears to be an internal communication or a directory update for that specific month.

articles.title: BULLETIN
articles.summary: This BULLETIN from the San Jose Amateur Astronomers outlines a challenging January with cancelled meetings and lease renewal issues, yet maintains optimism for future improvements. The club announces several upcoming events, including star parties and a general meeting in early 1976, and promotes its extensive library. Additionally, it congratulates member Dave Erickson on his astronomical photographs published in MERCURY.
